### Data Validation Results
| Field | Value | Valid | Issue |
|-------|-------|-------|-------|
| email | john@email | ❌ | Missing domain |
| phone | 555-1234 | ❌ | Only 7 digits |
| date | 2026-01-29 | ✅ | - |
